steps.name: User click on Start New Application
User click on Water Affecting Activity Permits
User click on Well Construction Permit Application
User click on Add new button
User fill the contact information page
User selects the location details and water supply type of well
User add attachment and reviews to record type
User pays the fees and click on next
User has successfully submit the application
